{"type": "article", "id": 51984, "title": "喜茶推出芒果色指甲油，Google 街景广告被黑 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-04-10T04:00:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 329, "name": "宝洁"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180410120644ZbzHTf3JP7NUogBW.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26614.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>陈冠希、窦骁出任科颜氏代言人</b></a>，为其全新科颜氏男士活力保湿系列造势。并分别发布两支广告片，挺好看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0625r1o9qv&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4ODIyNzcxMA==&amp;mid=2651103984&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=afc1882ed02584742fa8d85af78b018e&amp;chksm=8bdd68e1bcaae1f782dd80ce7f2db2025bbc4e336b1a3aa52065d223643dad000fecf04bf0af&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0410FBL9Ub1Wb2q5JHuJ6MFK&amp;key=8e58dd8e1c34471672c38b7f422d978f8ea0ea3116fd846d3c7233d927f4b80e36621a33be1fe89eaf0ee9c7c20cc51963ce588a7a35547770731ef83a4b9b11335e784b4d210f53cd5061a4b4e22ecc&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.13.4+build(17E199)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=D1YtA8mKEsnKIubwuCvEXFXQr9oruFz6BE9AgLb5ZhtPGh6msc2XcOhUCMScn0s1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">喜茶 X 小奥汀推出芒芒色指甲油</a></b>，一起发布的还有喜茶新品芒芒家族。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410111149kdL7o6TmYpnbFeJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.324374\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p id=\"owner-container\"><ytd-badge-supported-renderer></ytd-badge-supported-renderer></p><p><b><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqFzWxSCi39LnW1JKFR3efg\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saturday Night Live</a>&nbsp;的耐克假广告很好笑</b>：让我们承认女人买运动瑜伽裤不光是为了锻炼，更多时候就是穿着它在沙发上看电视，适合盖毯子放笔记本电脑的散热性能，方便用来擦你吃薯片的手指的材质……</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0626zmdd6p&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.jiemian.com/article/2043151.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 街景里的户外广告牌被无国界记者组织黑了</b></a>。他们把全球几个主要街区的广告牌，在 Google 街景中替换成了自己的宣传内容。</p><p class=\"\">在对 LGBT 人群持相当保守态度的俄罗斯?<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410105125klUbq7BrNAPm3F8E.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576182\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">“喜欢同性是正常的事 (Being gay is normal)”</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410105224QTHK6PMqOrkScpog.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.499133\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">印度：是“女人不该被当做第二阶级对待”</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018041010531246oVwP9KQGLjU8tE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.497400\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">津巴布韦：“我们正被一个自私的疯子领导着”</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">纽约时代广场的广告牌也换了：“是俄罗斯帮你赢得了大选，特朗普”。这句话引用自一个在 Twitter 发言影射俄罗斯影响美国大选的记者，她因此被特朗普拉黑。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410105428F6bS8rXM7gPvnZET.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.493934\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">瑞典著名创意机构 Åkestam Holst 为无国界记者组织设计了创意，他们将 Photoshop 处理后的照片上传至 Google 街景，试图用这种方式唤起对独立新闻和新闻自由的关注。当然，这是违反 Google 规则的，这些照片不会存在太久。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2018/04/09/product-red-iphone-8-ad/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苹果发布 iPhone 8 RED 版本官方视频广告</b></a>，苹果 apple.com 的主页也都变成了红色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0626yoc9u4&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.fastcompany.com/40556377/heres-why-sesame-street-is-turing-to-kickstarter-for-the-first-time?utm_source=feedly&amp;utm_medium=webfeeds\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>芝麻街落地 Kickstarter 项目</b></a>，主题是防止自闭症儿童被欺负，准备做儿童向的图书。这是芝麻街工作室第一个众筹项目，因为芝麻街工作室过去都依靠周边收入、捐款维持。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410110620qdoIgayAi7zS504M.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/p-g-to-bring-ad-holding-company-rivals-together-to-form-new-creative-agency-1523277000\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宝洁希望进一步改造和代理机构的关系</b></a>：计划从不同的广告集团内部抽调人手重新建立一家新的广告公司——这家包含阳狮旗下 Saatchi＆Saatchi、WPP 旗下 Grey 和宏盟旗下两家创意广告公司员工的新公司将搬到宝洁纽约和辛辛那提的总部一起办公，负责人是 Saatchi＆Saatchi 纽约的 CEO，新公司目前尚未命名。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：rimowa</p>"}